    </details>

    <details>
        <summary>What is the process for scheduling a viewing of a car?</summary>
        <p>To schedule a viewing of a car, simply contact the seller through phone or email.</p>
    </details>
    <details>
        <summary>Can I trade-in my current car for one of the listed cars?</summary>
